Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实故事改编
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血糖正常\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}blood glucose fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肝肾功能正常\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Liver function, kidney function,normal{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血小板数量正常\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Platelet count normal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血红蛋白正常\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}hemoglobin levels normal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血压 131/92\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}blood pressure, 131 over 92{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不高吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Isn't that high?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体重正常\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Weight fine{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰围最好再少一两公分\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}could do with losing a centimetre or two of your waist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大便样本未定\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Stool sample outstanding{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 意思是你还没提供给我们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No, that means you haven't provided one yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的 我想起来了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh yes. No, I'd remember{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得不难闻是吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you think it didn't stink or something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身体没什么问题 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There's basically nothing wrong with you Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太太告诉我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And your wife tells me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心自己有点抑郁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you think you're mildly depressed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被解雇了 失业中\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I got a sack. I'm unemployed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可那不是你的错 不是吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But it wasn't your fault, was it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这大概就是我抑郁的原因\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's probably why I'm depressed -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我压根就没说过的话被解雇\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I was sacked for saying something I didn't say!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试跑步\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Try running{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是子虚乌有\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I said the exact opposite of what I was sacked for!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在忙些什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What are you working on at the moment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑写一本书\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I was thinking of writing a book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 关于什么的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's good. What about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯历史\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Russian history.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着跑步吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Try running{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运输部长斯蒂芬·拜尔斯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The Whitehall feud between the transport secretary Stephen Byers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与前任新闻秘书马丁·西克史密斯之间的争执 继续发酵\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and the former press secretary Martin Sixsmith continues to grow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西克史密斯先生已经就这一纠纷发表自己的观点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Mr Sixsmith has been putting his side of the argument.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐宁街形容这起事件为一场肥皂剧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Downing Street described the affair as a soap opera.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有迹象表明西克史密斯先生今天在家中\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There was no sign of Mr Sixsmith at his home today{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在私下里试图证明自己的清白 一周之后\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}after a week trying to clear his name in private{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他如今要把事情公开\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's now gone public{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉星期日时报\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He told The Sunday Times{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府的高级官员向他表示支持\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}the senior figures in government had offered him their support{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们向我担保 他们承认\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They assured me they accepted{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无疑有针对我的不公正行为\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}there was no suspicion of misconduct against me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时非常震惊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I was therefore amazed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们单方面解雇我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}they had unilaterally resigned me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就马丁·西克史密斯先生离职一事作出声明\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'd like to make a statment regarding the circumstances of Mardin Sixsmith's resignation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是 布莱尔先生打算袖手旁观多久\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The quesion is how long Mr Blair stand by his man and not himself be damaged{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问这又是一个令政府尴尬的事件\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There's no doubt that there's been yet another embarrassment of the government{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不仅要吞下这个奇耻大辱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They've not only had to eat fantastic quantities of humble pie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这种屈辱还带有卑躬屈膝的意味\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}indeed humble pie I would say, with a side order of grovel sauce{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太尴尬了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That was embarrassing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼神父问我你去哪儿了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Father Tunney asked me where you disappeared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不相信上帝 他应该能看出来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well, I don't believe in god.I think he can tell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Come on{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm worried about you.Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跑步了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I did that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此 你需要回去工作\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I wish you had.You need to get back to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本俄罗斯历史的书怎样了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What happened to that book on Russian history?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人会对该死的俄罗斯历史感兴趣\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No one is interested in Russian bloody history{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}翻译/时间轴 JokerChow\N个人制作 请勿商用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前没见过你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Haven't seen you any place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Where're you from?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从利默里克来吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Are you from Limerick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello, Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近来可好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}How are you been?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你新换的髋关节怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}How's your new hip?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 是钛合金的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh, it's very good,it's titanium.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有段日子没见你了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Haven't seen you for a while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来点根蜡烛\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I just came into and light a candle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为某个特殊的人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Someone special?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的裙子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I like your dress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you make it yourself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我从店里买的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No I bought it in a shop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姑妈不让我跟你这样的陌生人说话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anyway, me auntie told me I'm not to talk to strange men like you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让他碰你了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you let him put his hands on you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很享受你的罪孽吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you enjoy your sin{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把短裤脱下了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you take your knickers down?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答希尔德嘉德修女 脱了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Answer Sister Hildegarde,did you take them down?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,院长修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Reverend Mother,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校从没告诉过我们怀孩子是怎么回事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}the school never told us anything about babies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲没跟你说过吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did your mother not tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她母亲十年前去世了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Her mother died ten years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}God rest her soul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怪修女们无情\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But don't dare to blame the sisters!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耻辱是你自己造成的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You are the cause of this shame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤风败俗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You and your indecency!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么办\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't know what to do!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须找个医生\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We must to get a doctor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婴儿的方向不对 这是臀位\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The child is the wrong way round. it's breech!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在上帝的掌握中\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's in God's hands now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦是她的赎罪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The pain is her penance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天主圣母,仁慈之母\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hail, Holy Queen, Mother of Mercy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们把我的孩子丢在外面\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Don't let them put my babay in the ground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面太冷太黑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's cold there,it's dark there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半小时之内帮他们关上灯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Just go up and turn their lights out in half an hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她难道不知道你有正经的工作\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Doesn't she know you've got a proper job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她缺人手 我只是代个班\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She's short staffed,just fill in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我午夜之前回来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'll be home before midnight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈 怎么了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What is it mum?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Are you alright?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Who's he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是他生日 他50岁了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's his birthday,he will be 50 today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个男孩\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's a boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh,Martin!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 大卫\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh,hello David{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯你认识的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Keith you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉·米契尔\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sally Mitchell{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是马丁·西克史密斯 曾经是BBC驻莫斯科记者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}this is Martin Sixsmith, used to be the BBC's man in Moscow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有华盛顿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And Washington.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还当过政府的高级顾问\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And then became a spin doctor for the government,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到后来出了点岔子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}until it all went a bit tits up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样总结恰当吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Is that a fair summation Martin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很恰当\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's fair enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常说 常在河边走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I always say if you shovel shit for long enough,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪能不湿鞋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}eventually you'll get some on your shoes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你连头都湿了 怎么弄的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes,you got it on your head,how did you manage that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你目前在做什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What are you up to at the moment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正考虑写一本俄罗斯历史的书\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm thinking of writing a book. On Russian history{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者别的 也许重回新闻界\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Or something else. Maybe get back to journalism{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I remember you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你写了那封糟糕的电子邮件\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You're the one who sent that terrible e-mail saying{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说911是个掩埋坏消息的好日子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it was a good day to bury bad news on 911{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是别人写的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No,I don't.That was someone else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I thought it was you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个普遍的误解\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's a common mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一年之后 玛格丽特公主葬礼那天\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}a year later, on the day of Princess Margaret's funeral{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发了封电邮说\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I send an e-mail saying{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们确定一下\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}let's make sure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天唯一"埋葬"的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}the only thing we "bury" inverted commas today{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是玛格丽特公主\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}is Princess Margaret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,略有区别\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's slightly different.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,区别大了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's very different.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果想重回新闻界\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well if you want to get back into journalism,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和莎莉谈谈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you should talk to Sally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我只是做\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh I just do, you know,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤感故事 情感类的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}sob stories, human interest stuff{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见得合你口味\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}not really your cup of tea is it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我倒很愿意看一看\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But I'll be happy to have a look{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有什么好的想法\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}if you want to push any ideas my way?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes please{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一杯灰皮诺\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Excuse me, a glass of Pinot Grigio?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有红葡萄酒和白葡萄酒\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's just red or white.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白葡萄酒\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh White please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心听到你是位记者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I couldn't help over hearing you were a journalist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识一个女人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I know a woman,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她未成年时生下一个孩子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and she had a baby when she was a teenager{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密她守了五十年\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she kept it a secret for fifty years{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想查清楚\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I need found out today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些修女把孩子从她身边带走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sorry,the baby was taken from her by these nuns{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强行送去收养\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}then they made her have it adopted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直守着这个秘密\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And she kept it a secret all this time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我目前正在写一本书\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm working on a book at the moment{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于俄罗斯历史\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}about Russian history{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙于这个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's my thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲的这件事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}what you're talking about would be{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是情感类题材\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}a human interest story,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不做这个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为情感故事是一种委婉的说法\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Because human interest story is euphemism for{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写的都是那些脆弱 胆怯 无知的人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}stories about vulnerable, weak-minded, ignorant, people{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用来填补报纸版面\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}to fill up the pages of newspapers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受众是那些脆弱 胆怯 无知的人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}read by vulnerable, weak-minded, ignorant people{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Not that you are{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 祝愿你能找到他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and,anyway,I hope you find him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是写个情感故事怎样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Do you think if I do a human interest story?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 你一定是菲洛梅娜了 我是马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello I'm Martin, you must be Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的位子在那边\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}we got a table through here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左边\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}just the left{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要为那晚道歉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I must apologize the other night,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时状态很糟\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}caught me at a bad moment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 很高兴你设法找到我了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That'alright,I'm just glad you managed to track me down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你别介意来这里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hope you don't mind coming here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妈最喜欢的餐厅\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it's mum's favourite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这地方很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh no it's very nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜 你好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So Philomena how are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去年做了髋关节置换手术\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I had a hip replacement last year Martin,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比之前好多了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it's much better than the bone one I had before{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是钛合金的 不会腐蚀\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and it's ti-tanium so it wouldn't rust.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错 你应该像铁皮人那样给它上油\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's good job you'd ought to have it oiled like the Tin Man{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh is that right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是说 像绿野仙踪里那样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No no,I mean, like the Wizard of Oz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是开玩笑 妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's just joking mum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It was just a joke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲双腿膝盖都患了晚期关节炎\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}My mother has advanced osteoarthritis in both her knees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来点沙拉吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Shall we get some salad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Salad,yes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简是我们家最聪明的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Jane's the clever one in our family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她作为一个成人学生进了大学\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She went to university as a mature student{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比应届生年龄大\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you know, when you're quite old.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上的什么大学 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Where did you go Martin{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是牛桥\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oxbridge I'll bet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你调侃我吗 是牛津\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You've ramble me.Oxford yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你不是笨蛋\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I knew you weren't a duffer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前去过Harvester餐厅\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've been a while in a Harvester before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在伦敦也有店吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Do they not have them in London?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 我喜欢在我住处附近用餐\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No I tend to go to a little local place, near where I live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And where's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士桥\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Knightsbridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定很贵\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh well that must be expensive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢在上面加一些吐司丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I love these pieces of toast on mine{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你结婚了吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And are you married Martin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 和凯特结婚二十年了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes. I am, to Kate.20years{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}that's good. That's grand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 我很爱他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I did love him, you know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把这些事在心里埋藏了五十年\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've kept what happened to me buried away for 50 years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲把我交给修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}My father just left me with the nums.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他觉得很丢脸 告诉别人我死了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He was so shamed,he told everyone I was dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家人从没去看过我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}My family never visit me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生下孩子之后\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}After you'd had your baby{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要在修道院待四年\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you had to stay in the Abbey for four years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了偿还收留你的修女们\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}In order to repay the sisters for taking you in,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须干活\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you had to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最差的是洗衣房的工作\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The worst jobs were in the laundry,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就被送到那里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and that's where they put me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周干活七天\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I worked there seven days a week,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年我一直在那\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}the whole time I was there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和最要好的朋友凯瑟琳一起干活\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I worked there with my best friend,Kathleen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天允许我们见孩子一个钟头\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We were allowed to see our children for an hour a day,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}that was all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走 不许跑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Walk don't run!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈咪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Mummy!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼和凯瑟琳的女儿玛丽是最好的朋友\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony was best friends with Kathleen's daughter Mary{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他俩形影不离\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The two of them were inseparable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 他一步都不肯离开她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Look at that, he won't let her out of his sight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厨房的女孩告诉我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Phil the girl in the kitchen said{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芭芭拉修女今天把玛丽带到那个房间\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Mother Barbara had Mary up at the house today{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她想对她做什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}what do you think she wanted with her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会有事的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sure it's nothing to worry about{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It won't be a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲儿 我现在有空\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Phil,I got some free{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳担心死了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Kathleen's worried sick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她觉得 他们要把玛丽带走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She thinks they're going to take Mary away from her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她如果他们要那么做的话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I told her if they were going to do that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会事先告诉她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}they'd tell her first for sure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别告诉任何人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you can't tell anyone about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸一定很英俊\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'll bet his father was handsome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么办到的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}How did you get this{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我借了一架布朗尼相机\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I borrowed a Box Brownie and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁院长不注意时拍的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}took it when Reverend Mother wasn't looking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Thank you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当我看着安东尼的照片时\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Whenever I look at that Anthony,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都为安娜希尔塔默默祈祷\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I say a little prayer for Anunciata,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她帮我接生 救了孩子一命\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}who saved his life when I gave birth to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很久前就去世了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She died a long time ago,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是她拍照 我什么也没有\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}If she hadn't taken that, I'd have nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一直被困在那里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So you were just trapped there the whole time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,付他们一百英镑才能离开\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}If you leave, you should pay them a hundred pounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上哪弄这笔钱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But where would I get that kind of money?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又去哪儿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And where would I go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天的情景我记得很清楚\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I remember that day so clearly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都明白那辆大轿车一到 意味着什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We all knew what it meant when a big car arrived.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳伤心欲绝\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Kathleen was inconsolable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道这次轮到玛丽了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She knew this time they'd come for Mary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开那里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Come away from there!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What are you doing out here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子疼 希尔德嘉德修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I had a stomach ache, Sister Hidegarde.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来例假了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's my time of the month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是只有你一人这样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well,you're not unique in that regard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把心思放工作上就过去了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Put your mind to your work and it'll pass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲儿 唱诗班练习开始了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Phil, it's choir practice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不去你就有麻烦了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You'll be in trouble if you don't go{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我通常喜欢唱歌\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Normally, I loved to sing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 为数不多能让我感到开心的事之一\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it was one of the only things I enjoyed at that place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我脑子里全是可怜的凯瑟琳\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But all I could think about was poor Kathleen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜 他们把安东尼带走了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Philomena,they take Anthony,they take him away!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Where's he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们原本只想接走玛丽\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They only come for Mary,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是安东尼一步都不愿离开她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but Anthony wouldn't let her out of his sight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不可分离\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They were inseparable{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对你做的一切太罪恶了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I think what they did to you was evil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 我不喜欢这个词\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No I don't like that word.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 罪恶很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No,evil's good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就故事而言\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Story wise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些修女 人很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Some of them were nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时是臀位分娩\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It was a breech birth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们连止痛药都不给她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and they wouldn't even give her painkillers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Excellence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是就故事而言\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Again,story wise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能找那些修女谈谈吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So can we go and talk to these nuns?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以试试\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We could try,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你比我妈运气好点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}maybe you'll have more luck than mum's had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些年我几次向他们打听他在哪里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've been several times over the years to ask where he was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很热心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They were very helpful{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟过去不一样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it's not like it used to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说 会试着帮我追寻他的下落\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They said they'd try and trace him for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们没有\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But they haven't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我找到他吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Can you help me find him Martin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是个很有趣的故事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well, it's an very interesting story.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周我要带妈妈去爱尔兰几天\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm taking mum to Ireland next week for a few days{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不如跟我们一起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}why don't you come along with us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以和她一起去罗斯克里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and you can visit Roscrea with her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的车很宽敞\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh yes there's plenty of room{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沃克斯豪尔骑士\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it's a Vauxhall Cavalier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 谢谢你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh no, I mean thank you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢坐飞机\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I like to fly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 抱歉我迟到了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello, sorry I'm a little late.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,租的车出了点问题\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Bit of trouble with the hire car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好 不是吗 简\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh it's lovely, isn't it Jane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白你为何不愿意跟我们挤骑士车了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I can see why you wouldn't want to squash up with us in the Cavalier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No.It wasn't that,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是还有其他的事要办\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it was just had a few things to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不让我一起去 妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Are you sure you don't want me to come with you mum?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不一起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You're not coming?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们俩去就行了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No,I told Jane we'll be fine on our own,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我们俩 是吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}just the two of us, isn't that right Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes. Fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把零食放你包里了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've put some things in your bag.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Thanks Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么车\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What kind of car is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝马\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's a BMW.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国车\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's German.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃块Tune吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Would you like a Tune Martin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哼歌 你伴奏吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}If I hum it, will you play it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}Tune 一种糖 有"曲子"之意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你想吃块Tune吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No, would you like a Tune?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能带来好运\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}For good luck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候一直以为\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I always thought{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣克里斯多夫有点像米老鼠\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Saint Christopher was a bit of Mickey Mouse Saint{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前是辅祭儿童\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I used to be an altar boy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 你相信上帝吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Do you believe in God Martin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well, where do you start.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为很难\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I always thought that's a very difficult question{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给出一个简单的回答\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}to give a simple answer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}do you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}罗斯克里修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.32,0:24:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You all right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.09,0:24:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.88,0:24:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸运 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm one of the lucky ones Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些母亲和孩子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Some of the mothers and babies{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分娩时都没活下来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}didn't even survive the childbirth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要什么帮助吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Can I help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲洛梅娜·李\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm Philomena Lee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.04,0:24:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前预约过\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I made an appointment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh yes come in Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我朋友马丁·西克史密斯 十点新闻的记者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And this is my friend Martin Sixsmith News At Ten.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.66,0:24:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是BBC 但我已经不在那了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}BBC news actually, but not any more{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.44,0:24:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh, hello{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.62,0:25:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱尔修女马上就到\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Claire will be with you shortly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.05,0:25:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能用下洗手间吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}May I use the bathroom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在楼下的...\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's down stairs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.36,0:25:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在哪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I know where it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们倒点茶好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Would I give you both some tea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.89,0:25:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes,thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.45,0:25:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}希尔德嘉德修女肖像 1957年10月
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.49,0:25:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}芭芭拉院长和希尔德嘉德修女\N在罗斯克里修道院外
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.89,0:25:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}我所有的爱 简
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.55,0:26:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.43,0:26:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.49,0:27:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.44,0:27:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh, hello.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.98,0:27:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克莱尔修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sister Claire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.88,0:27:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才在欣赏简·曼斯菲尔德的照片\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I Just admiring your picture of Jayne Mansfield.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.71,0:27:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是简·拉塞尔\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No that's Jane Russell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}两人皆为好莱坞黄金时代女星
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.74,0:27:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简·曼斯菲尔德是金发\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Jayne Mansfield was the blonde one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.76,0:27:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 她们名气都很大\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Of yes of course, I mean they were both very big{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.71,0:27:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们两人 都有很辉煌的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I mean the two of them, they were huge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.63,0:27:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演艺生涯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Their careers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.55,0:27:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个死于车祸来着\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Which one died in the car crash?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.09,0:27:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简·曼斯菲尔德\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Jayne Mansfield, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.66,0:27:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么挂她的照片\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why is she on the wall?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.05,0:27:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我没听清你的名字\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sorry, I didn't catch your name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.70,0:27:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 西克史密斯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Martin Sixsmith.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.84,0:27:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁·西克史密斯 十点新闻\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's Martin Sixsmith, News At Ten.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在BBC工作 但现在不是了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I was in BBC. But I'm not any more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 菲洛梅娜 非常高兴见到你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello Philomena, very nice to meet you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.41,0:27:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克莱尔修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sister Claire{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.68,0:27:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜 你上次来这里是什么时候\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What was the last time you came to see us Philomena?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.77,0:27:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在你来之前 克莱尔修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It was well before your time Sister Claire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.29,0:27:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟希尔德嘉德修女通了电话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I spoke to Sister Hildegarde on the telephone,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.26,0:27:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我到这里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and when I came here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.25,0:27:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她身体不好 不能和我见面\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she wasn't well enough to see me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.93,0:27:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还在这里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She's still with us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.87,0:27:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但非常虚弱\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but she's very frail now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:28:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 吃点黄油果子面包\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh Martin, Have some buttered brack.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.39,0:28:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美味 有点像潘多尔切\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Very nice, like a sort of a Pandolce{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.61,0:28:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是水果面包 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's fruit bread Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道 非常好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes, I know it's lovely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.02,0:28:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道上次他们有没有告诉你 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well now I don't know if they told you last time Philomena,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们绝大多数的档案\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but most of our records{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.30,0:28:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都毁于一场火灾\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}were destroyed in the big fire-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火灾\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Fire?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.10,0:28:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我来之前\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It was before my time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.43,0:28:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 恐怕我无法提供任何信息\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So I'm afraid I have no news.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.06,0:28:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直去做弥撒\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I still go to mass{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.08,0:28:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想造成什么麻烦\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't want to cause any fuss{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.00,0:28:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是指责谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}or point the finger at anybody,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.44,0:28:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或以任何方式怪罪教会\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}or blame the church in any way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道他是否还安好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I just want to know that he's all right{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.15,0:28:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至都不用见他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't even need to see him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.65,0:29:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能想象出\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I have visions of him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.95,0:29:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他无家可归的样子 没人疼爱他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and he's homeless and nobody loves him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Philomena{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.91,0:29:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法抚平你的创伤\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}we can't take away your pain,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们能和你携手度过难关\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but we can walk through it with you, hand in hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些老修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}these older nuns{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.73,0:29:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打断一下\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sorry interrupt{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.50,0:29:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们也许能回忆起一些细节\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Perhaps they might remember a few details?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多数都已经过世了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Most of them have passed away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.31,0:29:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些在世的呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What about the ones that haven't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.41,0:29:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不大可能和她们沟通\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't think you'll get much sense out of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.70,0:29:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能试一试吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Can We try?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这不可能\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't think that's going to be possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.99,0:29:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意回答菲洛梅娜提出的任何问题\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm happy to answer any questions that Philomena has.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.35,0:29:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问问题\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm asking a question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.75,0:29:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你是记者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You're a journalist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.87,0:29:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I used to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.65,0:29:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁是天主教徒\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Martin's a Roman Catholic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.41,0:29:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 嗯 曾经是\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes,well, I used to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和菲洛梅娜单独谈 我会觉得更自在点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'd feel more comfortable if I could speak to Philomena in private.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.07,0:30:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 有什么能帮你的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello,can I help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.61,0:30:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我只是在\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sorry, I was just erm...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.93,0:30:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么东西吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Are you looking for something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.12,0:30:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's down here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.42,0:30:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是私人住所\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Those are private quarters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.09,0:30:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面等\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'll wait outside{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}分娩时死亡的母亲和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.27,0:31:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}艾丝琳·德夫林 14岁 安息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我刚在周围转转\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sorry I was just having a look around{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.65,0:31:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跟你说了什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What did she say to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.75,0:31:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说你是个记者\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She said you were a journalist{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.95,0:31:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and you were trying to manipulate me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.81,0:31:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你说话要小心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I should be careful what I say to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.48,0:31:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还给了我这个\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She also gave me this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.05,0:31:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想亲自打开吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Don't you want to open it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.71,0:32:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一份你签字的协议 1955年\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's a contract signed by you,in 1955.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.84,0:32:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"我在此永久放弃对我的孩子安东尼·李的全部权利\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I hereby relinquish full claim forever to my said child Anthony Lee{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.43,0:32:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证绝不企图去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and I further undertake never to attempt to see,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.92,0:32:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看望 干涉 向这个孩子提出任何要求\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}interfere with or make any claim to the said child{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在将来的任何时刻"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}at any future time"{\r}
