Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.93,1:09:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还可以延期还这一万英镑\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and I can have an extension for ten thousand pounds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.79,1:09:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友蕾妮就贷过\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}my friend Rene did that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.18,1:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她为了修暖房\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she had a conservatory built.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.16,1:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要暖房\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't need a conservatory{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.69,1:09:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把钱还给你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and I could give you the money{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.40,1:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,付清所有机票和宾馆的开销\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}to cover the cost of all the flights and the hotel rooms{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.08,1:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不会有损失\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}then you won't be out of pocket and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.71,1:09:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的故事也不必发表\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you won't have to publish the story{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.11,1:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想发表\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}because I don't want it published{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.28,1:09:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远不想让任何人知道这件事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't want anyone to know about this, ever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.38,1:09:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有任何错\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You haven't done anything wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.34,1:09:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有权知道你儿子是谁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You are entitled to know who your son was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.01,1:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到玛丽说的话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well, you heard what Mary said{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.40,1:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他从来都没想过我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she said he never gave me a second thought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.34,1:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我的安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He wasn't my Anthony{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.54,1:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是别人的迈克尔\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}he was somebody else's Michael.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.30,1:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概他一想到我就生厌吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He probably hated the thought of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.01,1:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You don't know that Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.30,1:09:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该一直把他留在身边\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I should never have let him out of my sight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.08,1:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该和皮特·奥尔森谈谈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We need to talk to Pete Olssen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.21,1:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello yes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.87,1:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和皮特·奥尔森安排见面\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm trying to set up a meeting with Peter Olsson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.93,1:10:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打了几次电话\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes I've called a couple of times{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.61,1:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人回我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but no-one's calls me back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.06,1:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在碰壁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I feel like I'm hitting a bit of a brick wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.35,1:10:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没错 如果你把他的私人电话号码给我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes yes. But if you give me a personal number{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.60,1:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就行了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I think it's OK with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.07,1:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但我不明白为何他拒绝见我和菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes,but I don't understand why he refuses me and Philomena{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.10,1:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一小时\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}for just an hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.76,1:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛梅娜 你还好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Philomena are you alright?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.81,1:10:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 先生 没人接\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry sir,no answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.15,1:11:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能自己出门\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she wouldn't have gone anywhere by herself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.01,1:11:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能没什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It probably nothing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.91,1:11:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是个年龄很大的爱尔兰人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but she is quite old and Irish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.84,1:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是她亲属吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And she's a relative?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.90,1:11:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非亲属 否则不能让您进去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Cos I can't let you in unless she's a relative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.12,1:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她是我母亲\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes.She's... my mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.89,1:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门房\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Concierge{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.79,1:11:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲儿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Phil?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.37,1:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Mum{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.37,1:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.43,1:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Mum?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.14,1:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这儿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There you are!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.92,1:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.96,1:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到处找你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I wondered where you were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.13,1:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您母亲还好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Is your mother okay now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.19,1:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 谢谢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes, thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.83,1:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能这样说 他才让我进\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I had to say that to get him to let me in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.62,1:11:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该关阳台门\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You shouldn't have the balcony door shut{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.33,1:11:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面敲门就听不见了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}if you can't hear the door to the room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.53,1:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是出来哭一会 就这样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I was just out here having a little cry, that's all{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.33,1:11:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.67,1:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进屋吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You need to came inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.41,1:11:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会认为我想跳楼吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You didn't think I was going to jump off the balcony?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.36,1:11:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.98,1:12:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和皮特·奥尔森联系上了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Did you get through Pete Olsson?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.25,1:12:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打到他的办公室 他不在\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Just his office,he wasn't there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.59,1:12:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是不想见我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He just don't wanna see me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.96,1:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人不愿意面对过去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Some people have problems dealing with the past{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.87,1:12:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是针对你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}not you though,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.68,1:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他会接受的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sure he'll come around{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.80,1:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的座驾备好了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Your chariot awaits{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.83,1:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它漆成黄色了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I got it in yellow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.14,1:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 有些事我想跟你说\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Martin, there's something I have to say to you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.05,1:13:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've made a decision and my mind's made up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.94,1:13:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么都不会让我改变主意\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and there's nothing you can say that's going to make me change it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.52,1:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你为我做的一切\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I appreciate everything you've done for me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.10,1:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你照顾我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and thank you for looking after me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.36,1:13:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我享受了高级宾馆和美食 等等一切\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've enjoyed the hotels and all the food and everything,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.42,1:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这些都不是我想要的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but isn't worked out the way that I wanted it to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.55,1:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想明天就坐飞机回英国\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So, tomorrow I think we should get on an aeroplane and go back to England.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.98,1:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧 这就是结局\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There it is, and that's an end to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.95,1:13:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说那些有学问的话试图改变我的主意\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And don't try to change my mind by saying all clever things,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.54,1:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你上过牛桥 而我没有\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}just cos you went to Oxbridge and I didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.17,1:13:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉·米契尔呼叫\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sally Mitchell calling{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.28,1:13:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是牛津\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I went to Oxford{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.88,1:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛桥是牛津和剑桥的合成词\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oxbridge is a portmanteau of Oxford and Cambridge,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.94,1:13:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个词组合在一起的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}that's where two words join together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.18,1:14:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我特么...才不在乎呢\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't give a shi...shiny shoe about that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.55,1:14:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说都一样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it's all the same to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.94,1:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们去见皮特·奥尔森\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I think tomorrow we should go and visit Pete Olsson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.64,1:14:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去吧 我没准备好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Go on your own,I'm not prepered to go that way{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.96,1:14:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去听别人说我不在乎安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}to hear someone else tell me I didn't give two hoots about Anthony,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.67,1:14:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我抛弃了他云云\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and that I abandoned him and all the rest of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.26,1:14:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.28,1:14:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 -- 杯子上面\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What? -- On the side of the glass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.37,1:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔特竖琴\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's a Celtic harp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.81,1:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家 操自个儿的心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So I should go home and mind my own business,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.94,1:14:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看大卫·爱登堡的节目\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and watch David Attenborough on the tv{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.83,1:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会很开心的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and I'll be happy with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.00,1:14:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又是什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And what's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.46,1:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔特竖琴\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}A Celtic Harp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.66,1:14:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他根本不关心自己从哪儿来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why would someone cared so little about where he came from,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.31,1:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何还要戴爱尔兰胸针\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}wear something so Irish?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.50,1:14:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他弹竖琴 他是基佬\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Perhaps he played the harp? He was gay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.73,1:14:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不弹竖琴\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He didn't play the harp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.36,1:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}This is it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.17,1:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远没法给他这样的生活\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I couldn't have given him a life like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.14,1:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 你看 红色的马自达\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh look Martin - a little red Mazda.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.69,1:16:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他 皮特·奥尔森\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's him - that's Pete Olssen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.54,1:16:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在怎么办\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We what do we do now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.16,1:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门前插一脚\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We doorstep him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.14,1:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.27,1:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是下三滥记者的招数\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's that nasty journalists do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.69,1:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对付那些不配合采访的人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}when they want to speak to somebody who doesn't want to speak to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.36,1:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不了多久\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}This shouldn't take long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.28,1:17:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮特·奥尔森\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Peter Olssen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.80,1:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.02,1:17:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是马丁·西克史密斯\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm Martin Sixsmith,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.96,1:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和菲洛梅娜·李一起来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm here with Philomena Lee,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.21,1:17:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你已故的伴侣 迈克尔·赫斯的母亲\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}the mother of your late partner Michael Hess{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.28,1:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你个问题吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Can I ask you a question?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.66,1:17:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的脚从我门边拿开\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Can you get your foot out of my door?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.48,1:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hello?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.60,1:17:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 再不离开 我就叫警察了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sir,If you don't leave I'll call the police{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.66,1:18:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没帮上什么忙\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry.I've not been very helpful{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.85,1:18:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 至少你试过了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Never mind, at least you tried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.55,1:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Where are you going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.90,1:18:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Wait here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.55,1:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我家门口离开 要不我就\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Get off my property or I'll{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.70,1:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想和你谈谈我儿子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I just want to talk to you about my son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.77,1:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被人从我身边带走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He was taken from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.90,1:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也没见过他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And I've been looking for him ever since.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.46,1:21:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Would you look to him Martin{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.06,1:21:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Wait{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.35,1:21:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哪里不对\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's what? What's wrong?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.35,1:21:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去过爱尔兰\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He went to Ireland?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.28,1:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去过罗斯克里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He went to Roscrea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.35,1:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我带他去的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Yeah,I took him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.48,1:21:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在找你 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He was looking for you,Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.26,1:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个修女 我在罗斯克里见过\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That nun, I saw her at Roscrea{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.93,1:21:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔德嘉德修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Hildegard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.25,1:21:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经非常老了 但绝对就是她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She's very old now but it was definitely her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.08,1:21:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们一直告诉我没找到安东尼\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They always told me they didn't know where Anthony was{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.86,1:21:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她们告诉我们 没找到你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But they told us that they couldn't find you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.32,1:21:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们说你在他小时候抛弃了他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They said you'd abandoned him as a baby.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.50,1:21:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在找他儿子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She was looking for him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.81,1:21:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用了一辈子的时间在找他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}She's spent her whole life trying to find him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.66,1:21:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有抛弃我的孩子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I didn't not abandoned my child.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.28,1:22:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在就在那里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's there now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.01,1:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.05,1:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为这个和他爸争执\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I had this huge standoff with his father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.05,1:22:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爸想让他葬在美国\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He wanted him buried in the US,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.38,1:22:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是您儿子的遗愿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but it was your son's dying wish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.78,1:22:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想回家\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He said he wanted to go home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.48,1:22:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他葬在罗斯克里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's buried at Roscrea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.51,1:23:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兜了一个大圈子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We've come full circle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.18,1:23:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"出发了很久以后\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The end of all our exploring{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.77,1:23:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又回到起点\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}will be to arrive where we started,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.29,1:23:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里我们重新认识这个地方"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and know the place for the first time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.43,1:23:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 说的真好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh Martin that's lovely,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.55,1:23:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚想出来的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}did you just think of that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.59,1:23:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是TS·艾略特的诗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No, it's TS Eliot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.38,1:23:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 依旧很好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well never mind it's still nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.61,1:23:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以进去了吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Shall we go in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.86,1:23:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会进去大吵大闹吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You're not going to make a scene in there are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.01,1:23:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是问几个问题\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm just going to ask a few questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.73,1:23:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喝茶\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And I don't want any tea,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.41,1:23:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不吃点心\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and I don't want any cake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.39,1:24:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来 菲洛梅娜\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}do come in Philomena.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.36,1:24:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱尔修女请你等她\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Claire has asked if you could wait here for her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.49,1:24:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 马丁 不是她们的错\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Now remember Martin, it's not their fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.30,1:24:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们不知道安东尼还有另一个名字\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}They didn't know that Anthony had a different name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.53,1:24:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个人知道\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}One of the did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.71,1:25:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你在干什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Excuse me what do you think you're doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.12,1:25:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能来这里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You're not allowed here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.18,1:25:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他直接就闯进来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He just walked straight in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.16,1:25:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种行为太无礼了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}This is completely inappropriate behaviour!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.98,1:25:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔德嘉德修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Hildegarde.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.86,1:25:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来伤害你的\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm not here to hurt you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.10,1:25:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是问你一个问题\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've just come to ask you a question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.60,1:25:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲洛梅娜·李的朋友\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm a friend of Philomena Lee{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.43,1:25:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在一段视频里见过你和他儿子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I saw you on a video with her son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.16,1:25:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明知他们母子在互相寻找\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}When you knew they looking for each other,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.20,1:25:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉真相\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}why did you keep them apart?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.42,1:25:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要叫警卫了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}We're going to call the guards{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.46,1:25:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你立即离开\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}unless you leave immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.79,1:25:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不回答我的问题 我就不走\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm not leaving if she not answer my question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.35,1:25:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 你整个人的态度\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry I think your whole manner,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.77,1:25:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人作呕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}it is absolutely disgusting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.53,1:25:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你什么叫令人作呕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'll tell you what's disgusting,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.61,1:25:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对一个垂死之人说谎\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}lying to a dying man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.31,1:25:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本可以给他们一点点珍贵的时间\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You could have given them a few precious moments{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.26,1:25:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他死前和生母团聚\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}with his mother before he passed away{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.70,1:25:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你选择了说谎\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}but you chose not to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.28,1:25:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是令人作呕\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's disgusting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.21,1:25:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来 希尔德嘉德修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Come on Sister Hildegarde,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.17,1:25:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必听这些\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}you don't have to listen to this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.91,1:25:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是基督徒吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Not very Christian is it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.91,1:25:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Wait!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.33,1:26:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来告诉你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Let me tell you something{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.19,1:26:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宣誓终身守贞\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I have kept my vow of chastity my whole life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.73,1:26:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苦修禁欲\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Self denial and mortification of the flesh,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.44,1:26:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能更接近上帝\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}that's what brings us closer to God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.04,1:26:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些姑娘全是自己的错 怪不得任何人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Those girls have nobody to blame but themselves,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.75,1:26:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己无法克制肉欲\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and their own carnal incontinence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.45,1:26:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔德嘉德修女 求求你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Hildegarde - please!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.20,1:26:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说她们有性行为\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You mean they had sex?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.85,1:26:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的都已经过去\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What's done is done{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.85,1:26:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想叫我们怎样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}what do you expect us to do about it now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.69,1:26:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.07,1:26:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都无可挽回\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}There's nothing to be done{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.96,1:26:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里是为了看我儿子\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've found my son, that's what I came here for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.14,1:26:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.66,1:26:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我来告诉你该怎么做\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Hang on hang on.I'll tell youhat you can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.55,1:26:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说对不起 怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Say sorry. How about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.93,1:26:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道歉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Apologise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.77,1:26:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许再掩盖真相\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Stop trying to cover things up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.30,1:26:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去清理干净墓前的杂草\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Go out there and clear all the weeds and crap off the graves{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.27,1:26:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为那些死在这里的母亲和婴儿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}of the mothers and babies who died here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.48,1:27:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们的苦难是为了赎罪\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Their suffering was atonement for their sins{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.21,1:27:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个母亲才14岁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}One of the mothers was fourteen years old!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.64,1:27:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 够了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}That's enough Martin!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.55,1:27:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主耶稣基督会审判我\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}The Lord Jesus Christ will be my judge{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.55,1:27:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}not the likes of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.88,1:27:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 如果耶稣在这里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Really? Because I think if Jesus was here right now{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.77,1:27:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会把你从该死的轮椅里扔出来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}he'd tip you out of that fucking wheelchair{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.67,1:27:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都爬不起来\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and you wouldn't get up and walk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.66,1:27:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Stop it! Stop it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.06,1:27:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.01,1:27:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让他在这里大吵大闹\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I didn't want him to come in here like this and make a scene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.36,1:27:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗跟他们道歉\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why are you apologizing to them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.33,1:27:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼得艾滋快死的时候\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Anthony was dying of Aids{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.49,1:27:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她都不告诉他你在哪里\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and she still wouldn't tell him about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.75,1:27:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当事人是我 不是你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But it happened to me. Not you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.34,1:27:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做是我的事情\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}And it's up to me what to do about all this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.13,1:27:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我选择\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's my choice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.05,1:27:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就打算不了了之\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So you're just going to do nothing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.12,1:27:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}No{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.59,1:27:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔德嘉德修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Hildegarde,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.02,1:27:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你明白\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I want you to know that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.50,1:27:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原谅你了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I forgive you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.05,1:27:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 就这么完了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}What..? Just like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.70,1:27:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是"就这么完了"\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's not "just like that"!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.05,1:27:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一步对我来说很艰难\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's hard. It's hard for me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.50,1:28:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想记恨别人\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't want to hate people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.05,1:28:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想像你那样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I don't want to be like you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.52,1:28:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Look at you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.87,1:28:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很生气\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm angry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.75,1:28:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很累吧\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It must be exhausting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.73,1:28:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱尔修女\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Sister Claire,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.17,1:28:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你带我去看我儿子的墓好吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}would you be kind to take me to my son's grave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.08,1:28:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well,I couldn't forgive you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.33,1:29:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我已经冷静下来了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's alright.I'm calm down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.66,1:29:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想买点东西\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I just want to buy something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.61,1:30:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我会找到他\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He knew I'd find him here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.46,1:30:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会发表\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I'm not going to publish the story.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.51,1:30:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你和他的故事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}It's between you and him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.65,1:30:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你一样东西\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I got you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.71,1:30:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.11,1:30:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.30,1:30:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚决定了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}You know, I'd just decided{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.50,1:31:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,归根结底 还是想让你说出这个故事\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}that I did want you to tell my story after all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.17,1:31:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该让世人明白这里发生过什么\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}People should know what happened here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.17,1:31:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 我刚看完这本书\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Oh, Martin, I've just finished that book,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.01,1:31:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《马鞍和织布机》\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}"The Saddle and the Loom"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.94,1:31:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想读吗\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}would you like to read it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.53,1:31:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你直接讲给我听就好\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Why don't you just tell me about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.00,1:31:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个织布工\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Well there's this weaver,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.73,1:31:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她相当平凡\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}she's quite plain really,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.24,1:31:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮但是平凡 -我喜欢平凡的姑娘\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}pretty but plain. --I like plain girls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.79,1:31:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她被告知要整夜工作\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and she's told she has to work all through the night to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.33,1:32:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用上好的丝绸织出一件漂亮的披风\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}weave  a beautiful cloak of the finest silk{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.99,1:32:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给主人在他的婚礼上穿\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}for the master in his wedding day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.73,1:32:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天一早\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}So in the morning{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.96,1:32:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当她把织好的披风给他看\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and she shows him the cloak{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.81,1:32:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问他 先生你觉得怎么样\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}and asks him what do you think kind sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.68,1:32:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说道 真美\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}"it's beautiful{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.50,1:32:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这一生都没见过更美的了\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}I've never seen anything more beautiful in my whole life".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.00,1:32:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你猜怎么着\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}But guess what,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.08,1:32:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是在看披风\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}he's not even looking at the cloak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.90,1:32:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在看姑娘\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}He's looking at her{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.27,1:32:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马丁 我根本想不到这结局\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Martin! Well, I never saw that coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.70,1:32:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百万年都想不到\N{\fnTimes New Roman\fs13\3c&H000000&}Not in a million years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.41,1:32:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}马丁·西克史密斯于2009年出版\N《菲洛梅娜·李遗失的孩子》
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.62,1:32:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}上千被领养的爱尔兰孩子和他们"耻辱"的母亲\N仍在寻找彼此
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.62,1:32:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H000000&}菲洛梅娜·李和子孙住在英格兰南部\N她一直去看望儿子在罗斯克里的墓地
